results.title: ICECO Introduces APL Black Series: Built Tough for Every Adventure
results.description: BREA, Calif., March 18, 2025 /PRNewswire/ -- ICECO, a leading expert dedicated to providing innovative portable refrigeration solutions, proudly unveils the Matte Black edition of its APL20 and APL35 fridge freezers. Designed for overlanders, outdoor explorers, and off-road enthusiasts, these sleek new models combine ICECO's signature durability and performance with a modern aesthetic, ready for any terrain. ICECO INTRODUCES NEW APL ALUMINUM BLACK SERIES A Bold New Look for the Great Outdoors The APL20 and APL35 Black editions feature a striking matte black finish that not only looks premium but is built to withstand the toughest outdoor conditions. Crafted with a full aluminum, corrosion-resistant, and weatherproof body, these refrigerators are made for overlanders and off-road adventure seekers who demand reliability, durability, and style. Whether you're tackling rugged off-road trails or enjoying a weekend camping trip, the APL20 and APL35 Black are designed to enhance your outdoor experience. APL35 Black: Power and Performance in One Package Weighing just 32 lbs, the APL35 Black is easy to transport and fits perfectly in truck beds, even with an added cover. Its top-tier SECOP Nano compressor ensures rapid cooling, dropping temperatures from 77°F to 32°F in just 11 minutes (empty), and comes with a 5-year warranty. The refrigerator also features 27L + 8L dual-zone compartments, allowing independent temperature control to keep your food and drinks perfectly chilled or frozen at the optimal temperature. With a dual-cooling system, it can hold up to 57 cans, making it perfect for long trips or large gatherings. It also features a lid stay function that holds the lid open at any angle, preventing accidental injuries to children caused by the lid suddenly closing while they retrieve food or drinks. The Bluetooth APP allows for remote temperature control and monitoring, while the built-in magnetic patch makes it compatible with ICECO's 250WH magnetic battery, providing up to 11 hours of cooling on a single charge. APL20 Black: Compact and Convenient For solo adventurers or those with limited space, the APL20 Black offers a 21L single-zone cooling system that can hold up to 32 cans. Weighing just 22.9 lbs, this compact refrigerator is perfect for weekend getaways, office use, or as a portable cooler for day trips. Its lightweight design and sleek matte black finish make it an ideal companion for those who value portability without sacrificing style. No more soggy food or the hassle of melting ice with these advanced refrigeration solutions. These portable fridges allow users to enjoy ice cream on the go and keep beverages chilled even on the hottest days. Equipped with precise temperature control, the APL20 and APL35 Black ensure food stays fresh and healthy, while eliminating the need for ice bags frees up valuable space for more provisions. Whether on a remote trail or at a campsite, these units function as a portable home fridge, bringing the comfort of home-cooked meals to every outdoor adventure. The ICECO APL20 Black and APL35 Black portable refrigerators will be available for purchase starting March 21, 2025 on icecofreezer.com. Take advantage of early bird pricing with savings of up to 20% for a limited time. The product will be available for shipment to the USA (Except PR, HI, AK) and Canada (Except NT, YT, NU). About ICECO ICECO stands for innovation, quality, and unmatched customer support. With 100+ global technology patents and full in-house R&D and production capabilities, we're dedicated to crafting reliable portable fridges for every adventure. Trusted by outdoor enthusiasts worldwide, ICECO is your ultimate overland companion. Social Media:InstagramFacebookYouTubeTikTok

creator: Charles Kennedy
results.description: Despite high natural gas prices and increased LNG demand in Europe after the end of Russian pipeline gas, floating LNG import terminals in France and Germany have sat idle for months as the high cost of operating the floating units undermines their competitiveness compared to onshore facilities. One example of this situation is the Le Havre floating terminal, commissioned by France’s TotalEnergies in 2023 as part of emergency measures in response to the energy crisis following the Russian invasion of Ukraine. results.title: الإصابة تبعد كاسادو عن برشلونة لمدة شهرين
creator: اليوم- إسبانيا
results.description: تعرض لاعب وسط برشلونة مارك كاسادو لتمزق جزئي في رباط ركبته خلال الفوز الأخير على أتلتيكو مدريد، سيبعده عن الملاعب نحو شهرين بحسب ما ذكر متصدر الدوري الإسباني لكرة القدم الثلاثاء.وخاض ابن الحادية والعشرين 37 مباراة في مختلف المسابقات هذا الموسم ضمن تشكيلة المدرب الألماني هانزي فليك.وانسحب كاسادو بالتالي من تشكيلة المنتخب الإسباني التي تستعد لخوض ربع نهائي دوري الأمم الأوروبية ضد هولندا.وأجبرت الإصابة اللاعب الشاب على الخروج من الملعب في الدقيقة 67 من المباراة التي قلب برشلونة نتيجتها في الوقت القاتل وخرج فائزا 4-2 في قمة المرحلة الثامنة والعشرين من الدوري.قال برشلونة في بيانه "تأكد انه يعاني من تمزق جزئي في الرباط الجانبي لركبته اليمنى.. قد يغيب عن الملاعب نحو شهرين".ويتصدر برشلونة ترتيب الليغا بفارق الأهداف عن ريال مدريد الإسباني لكنه لعب مباراة أقل.تعادل مع أتلتيكو في ذهاب نصف نهائي الكأس، ويلاقي بوروسيا دورتموند الألماني الشهر المقبل في ربع نهائي دوري أبطال أوروبا.
